headline.main: No. 2 Baylor Rolls Into Women's Big 12 Tournament Semifinals
headline.print_headline: No. 2 Baylor Rolls Into Women's Big 12 Tournament Semifinals

lead_paragraph: Alexis Prince scored 22 points to help No. 2 Baylor coast to a 95-63 victory over Texas Tech on Saturday in the quarterfinals of the Big 12 Tournament.
